            {
                "s2_paper_id": "234915140207321577e7716f9b52db4fdd7459c8",
                "title": "On the automorphisms of a graph product of abelian groups",
                "year": 2007,
                "venue": "",
                "citation_count": 42,
                "reference_count": 30,
                "abstract": "We study the automorphisms of a graph product of finitely generated abelian groups W. More precisely, we study a natural subgroup Aut* W of Aut W, with Aut* W = Aut W whenever vertex groups are finite and in a number of other cases. We prove a number of structure results, including a semi-direct product decomposition Aut* W = (Inn W x Out(0) W) x Aut(1) W. We also give a number of applications, some of which are geometric in nature.",
